summary: An ordinance relating to and providing for the cost and expense of the condemnation of Louisa Street between Eastlake Avenue and Minor Avenue North, and of an alley between Yale Avenue North and Minor Avenue North, from the south line of Sample's Addition to the City of Seattle, to the true north line of Green's Addition to the City of Seattle, as provided in Ordinance No. 42959, and repealing Ordinance No. 45966.
